<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background: #f5f5f5; margin: 0; padding: 20px; }
    .card { background: #fff; border-radius: 8px; padding: 32px; max-width: 520px; margin: 0 auto; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
    .header { background: #742a2a; border-radius: 6px 6px 0 0; padding: 20px 32px; margin: -32px -32px 28px; }
    .header h1 { color: #fff; font-size: 18px; margin: 0; }
    .header span { color: #feb2b2; font-size: 14px; }
    .project-name { font-size: 22px; font-weight: bold; color: #1a1d2e; margin: 16px 0 8px; }
    .detail { color: #718096; font-size: 14px; margin: 6px 0; }
    .footer { margin-top: 28px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; font-size: 12px; color: #a0aec0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>🚀 DevTeam Hub</h1>
      <span>Project access update</span>
    </div>

    <p>Hi <strong><%= @user.display_name %></strong>,</p>

    <p>You have been <strong>removed</strong> from the following project by <strong><%= @removed_by.display_name %></strong>:</p>

    <div class="project-name">📁 <%= @project.name %></div>

    <p class="detail">You no longer have access to this project in DevTeam Hub.</p>

    <p class="detail">If you believe this is a mistake, please contact your team lead or system administrator.</p>

    <div class="footer">
      DevTeam Hub — automated project access notification.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
